original: Bäckström, John Stellan, tandläkare, Borås, f. 21/9/95 i Kristianstad av musikfanj. C. O. Bäckström o. Hilma Möller. G. 20 m. Gurli Eliasen. Barn: Gudrun f. 21, tandläk., Karl-Fredrik 22, d. 29, Sven-Eric 23, Glaes-Göran 26, Stina 36. — Stud:ex. i Ystad 14, tandhkand. 15, tandläk. 17. Praktik i Höganäs 17-18, assist, i Kristianstad 18-19, praktik i Borås -sed. 19.
translated: Bäckström, John Stellan, dentist, Borås, born on September 21, 1895 in Kristianstad, son of musician C.O. Bäckström and Hilma Möller. Married to Gurli Eliasen in 1920. Children: Gudrun, born in 1921 and also a dentist, Karl-Fredrik born in 1922 and deceased in 1929, Sven-Eric born in 1923, Glaes-Göran born in 1926, and Stina born in 1936. Studied in Ystad and graduated in 1914. Passed dental exams in 1915 and became a certified dentist in 1917. Practiced in Höganäs from 1917 to 1918, served as an assistant in Kristianstad from 1918 to 1919, and practiced in Borås from 1919 onwards.
